<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"/>
  <title>Welcome Email — Forever Yours</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #F1EDE6; font-family: Georgia, serif }
    .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #FFFFFF }
    .header { background: #141210; padding: 36px; text-align: center }
    .header img { height: 28px; width: auto }
    .hero-section { background: #F1EDE6; padding: 52px 48px; text-align: center }
    .eyebrow { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7C6A54; margin-bottom: 16px }
    .hero-section h1 { font-size: 36px; font-weight: normal; color: #141210; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 16px }
    .hero-section h1 em { font-style: italic; color: #7C6A54 }
    .hero-section p { font-size: 18px; font-style: italic; color: #6A6058; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 }
    .body-section { padding: 48px }
    .body-section p { font-size: 17px; font-style: italic; color: #6A6058; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0 0 20px }
    .body-section p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0 }
    .verse { background: #F8F6F3; border-left: 3px solid #7C6A54; padding: 24px 28px; margin: 32px 0 }
    .verse p { font-size: 18px; font-style: italic; color: #141210; line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 0 8px }
    .verse span { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9A9080 }
    .cta-section { padding: 0 48px 48px; text-align: center }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-block; background: #141210; color: #FFFFFF; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 18px 40px; text-decoration: none }
    .sig { padding: 0 48px 48px }
    .sig p { font-size: 17px; font-style: italic; color: #6A6058; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0 0 12px }
    .sig-name { font-size: 22px; font-style: italic; color: #7C6A54 }
    .footer { background: #F1EDE6; padding: 28px 48px; text-align: center }
    .footer p { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; color: #A09888; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 }
    .footer a { color: #7C6A54; text-decoration: none }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="{{ shop.url }}/cdn/shop/files/logo-black.png" alt="Forever Yours"/>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-section">
      <p class="eyebrow">Welcome</p>
      <h1>So glad you are<br/><em>here.</em></h1>
      <p>You just joined a community of people learning to hear God's voice and receive His love every single day.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="body-section">
      <p>Hi friend,</p>
      <p>My name is Rose and I am so grateful you found your way here. This community was born out of my own darkest season when I first encountered the love of Jesus and everything changed.</p>
      <p>Every Love Letter I share is written in God's first person voice because I believe He wants to speak directly to your heart. Not through religion or rules, but through love.</p>
      <div class="verse">
        <p>"I have loved you with an everlasting love. I have drawn you with unfailing kindness."</p>
        <span>Jeremiah 31:3</span>
      </div>
      <p>That is the heart behind everything I do. And I am so excited for you to be part of it.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-section">
      <p style="font-size:17px;font-style:italic;color:#6A6058;margin-bottom:24px;">If you haven't yet, start your 24 days with Jesus today.</p>
      <a href="{{ shop.url }}/products/forever-yours-24-days-with-jesus" class="cta-btn">Get Forever Yours</a>
    </div>
    <div class="sig">
      <p>With so much love,</p>
      <p class="sig-name">Rose Renuu</p>
      <p style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#9A9080;">@roserenuu &nbsp;·&nbsp; @jesusforeveryours</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>You are receiving this because you joined the Forever Yours community.<br/>
      <a href="#">Unsubscribe</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="{{ shop.url }}">jesusforeveryours.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>